- The goal for this sprint is to have our building blocks right and to have a solid initial structure, by meeting up with restaurants owners and getting a written approval from them to work with us, to prove that they are serious about the application, and we will demo for them a basic page from the application to prove our side of the deal.
- All team members are involved in this stage, and there will be no vacations or holidays during this sprint.
- I am confident that we will complete this sprint without major issues and it will be done on the specified time
- The duration for this sprint is 1 week.
